'''Cathay Pacific Limited''' ke lifofane tsoang [[Hong Kong]]. E tsamaisa batho le thepa kapa go e ka godimo go 120 metse lefatše ka bophara. Botlaaseng ya yona e kgolo kapa khubu ke ka Hong Kong International Airport. 

Ke e 'ngoe ea Airlines tse tšeletseng lefatšeng go fumana tse hlano stjernerangering tsoang Skytrax. E swarwile "Lifofane tša Ngwaga" khau tsoang Skytrax ka 2003, 2005 le 2009. Morali'abo rona e eona lifofane e '''Dragonair''' e leng o sebeletsa celow [[Tšhaena]] linaheng le [[Asia]].
